site_name:
Land At Great Suffolk Street Industrial Estate
5-7 Bear Lane
London
SE1 0UH
description: Demolition of existing buildings and erection of a new (maximum 8 storey, 28 metres high) building comprising of 89 dwellings, 776.5 sqm of general business floorspace (Class B1), 563.3 sqm of restaurant/bar (Class A3/A4), ancillary car parking (basement parking), servicing and amenity space and landscaping with vehicular access from Bear Lane.
